  "representativeCastDefIDOverride": "castDef_JoannaMcEvedy",
  "shortDescription": "Intelligence has identified a [[DM.Factions[faction_GhostBearWatch],Ghost Bear Watch]] forward surveillance post operating in an isolated region of St. Andreas. The facility has been coordinating intelligence gathering on [[DM.Factions[faction_MinnesotaTribe],Minnesota Tribe]] cell locations across the sector, feeding targeting data to Watch strike teams conducting operations against Tribe assets.\n\nReconnaissance shows heavy fortifications protecting the installation, including advanced turret emplacements and multiple lances of frontline combat units deployed in defensive positions. This level of military protection confirms the facility's high intelligence value to Watch command and suggests it may house critical surveillance infrastructure.\n\nRecent garrison rotation cycles have created a narrow operational window for assault. Primary objective is to capture the facility intact and extract all intelligence data from the central servers before Watch command can initiate remote purge protocols. Secondary objective is to secure any physical intelligence materials present at the site.\n\nExpected opposition includes heavy garrison forces with fortified defensive positions. The facility's remote location limits reinforcement potential but also means defenders will fight aggressively to prevent capture. Electronic warfare capabilities will be essential to prevent data destruction during the assault.",
  "longDescription": "Heavily fortified Watch outpost with serious garrison forces protecting it. We better move in fast and capture it, before they can react.",
  "salvagePotential": 16,
